{
  "texts": [
    "For example, if on the first interval Whisper transcribes the sequence s 1, s 2, s 3, s 4 and then on the second interval it transcribes s 1, s 2, s 3, s ′ 4, s 5, s 6, only the s 1, s 2, s 3 will be committed to the stable transcription.",
    "Once committed as a stable transcription, it becomes available to the Simultaneous Translation LLM Pipeline for translation.",
    "To further improve transcription quality, Whisper is also provided with additional context from a context buffer.",
    "The context buffer is designed to provide Whisper with the transcript from the previous segment.",
    "However, if the previous segment exceeds the cutoff threshold, the number of context words is limited to be equal to the cutoff threshold."
  ]
}